{"tid":2267591,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【奇人異事】有冇人係無任何興趣？","createTime":"2020-11-02T07:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T16:10:41.000Z","uid":342282,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e14db92a769b50c1242aca4036542ad41087710d","tid":2267591,"uid":342282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:42:25.000Z","msg":"由細到大對咩野都冇興趣<br />\n少朋友，無拍拖<br />\n唔鍾意籃球足球<br />\n唔睇波唔賭錢唔鍾意飲酒<br />\n唔鍾意買野近乎零物慾<br />\n對美食無要求，唔食零食炸野只係食清淡簡單野<br />\n只飲水，從來唔飲汽水咖啡奶茶甜野<br />\n唔煲劇唔睇戲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放假淨係會上網，睇下新聞，睇下wiki，睇下連登咁就一日<br />\n好似從來對生活提唔起勁，有冇人都係咁？"},{"pid":"50ea453a1ccdbf4a714c903f8b6d124f845a0ac8","tid":2267591,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"低欲望人生<br />\n現代版既城市隱士"},{"pid":"97f80a9b1567055147556fc9cdfae303c8631d9a","tid":2267591,"uid":342282,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"50ea453a1ccdbf4a714c903f8b6d124f845a0ac8","tid":2267591,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"低欲望人生<br />\n現代版既城市隱士"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"隱士係有技能有長處嘛<br />\n小弟讀書又唔叻，玩又唔叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2507e42534690b88c2e0a73b15f90beb91d88e6","tid":2267591,"uid":127425,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:46:27.000Z","msg":"唔試下打坐?"},{"pid":"98948ace9906f8e24e2a9cacd914708ce9ffca67","tid":2267591,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:47:10.000Z","msg":"唔鐘意藍足球唔睇波 唔飲唔吸 剩買六合彩<br />\n唔買衫唔買鞋"},{"pid":"0f989c5ae4bf9f8508aa020264c19b375cd969cf","tid":2267591,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"97f80a9b1567055147556fc9cdfae303c8631d9a","tid":2267591,"uid":342282,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"50ea453a1ccdbf4a714c903f8b6d124f845a0ac8","tid":2267591,"uid":118